# Linux Log Files

## Common Log Directory

```text
/var/log
```

## Important Logs

- syslog
- auth.log
- kern.log
- dpkg.log

## Useful Commands

```bash
ls /var/log
tail /var/log/syslog
tail -f /var/log/syslog
less /var/log/syslog
```

## Best Practice

Always review log files before changing system configurations.
